  "texts": [
    "The system prompt was \"Please act as a nurse specialist in breast cancer to assist me. \"",
    "All other parameters were maintained at default settings without modification.",
    "Three senior nurses with > 10 years of clinical experience (XRY, HY, and XHM) independently evaluated the 15 Q&A results from the GPT-4 and RAG-GPT groups.",
    "The primary evaluation endpoint was overall satisfaction, and the secondary endpoints were accuracy and empathy.",
    "The assessment used a Likert scale in which each endpoint was rated with a continuous numerical value from 1 to 10, with 1 indicating \"very dissatisfied, \" 5 representing \"neutral, \" and 10 denoting \"very satisfied. \""
  ],
